_sText:
This is a remake of my map de_highrise that I wanted to do for a while now. 

Compared to the other highrise, it doesn't have the "underground" kind of area and the bombsites. The fps are even better now and all the action is concentrated on top making this a good fy/aim combo,gg,dm map. 

It features HDR lighting (toned down compared to the original), 40 player spawns, soundscapes, overview, optimized and tweaked nav file, custom content.

I started making this the other day and then I saw that there's this contest going on so I thought to myself: Added bonus! :D

Have fun!

(Map's for CS:S)
